N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 1001.4 - Withdrawals of applications

State Regulations
(a) An application made to the fund pursuant
to law and in accordance with this Part may, on written request of the
applicant, be withdrawn, prior to decision by the fund at any time without
prejudice to resubmission. (b) When
an application is withdrawn, the original application and supporting documents
shall be returned to the applicant. Copies of the application and supporting
documents shall be retained in the office of the secretary of the
fund. Notes
